    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re your Dec. 31 and Jan. 1 editorials about the year 2000: I would like to add a factor that will profoundly affect the world to be: our understanding of the biological basis of life. We will soon possess the ability to manipulate life in ways that not too long ago were the essence of fantasy. How we come to grips with this godlike power may well be the central question of the new millennium.</p>
        <p>STEVEN H. SCHWARTZ  New York, Jan. 1, 2000</p>
      </block>
